for the past four years,

08:36.792 --> 08:39.125
and she's here with
her dad to talk about it.

08:39.457 --> 08:42.207
Tell us, when did you realize
that Tessa was first ill?

08:42.250 --> 08:43.832
Four years ago.

08:43.917 --> 08:45.917
