we thought it was the flu,

08:45.958 --> 08:47.250
Tessa's mum and I.

08:47.333 --> 08:49.917
But the flu just
wouldn't clear up.

08:50.625 --> 08:52.625
The blood test
confirmed our worst fears.

08:52.708 --> 08:54.292
The doctors told
us they couldn't

08:54.417 --> 08:56.000
hold out any hope
for her survival,

08:56.083 --> 08:57.542
which brought us
to the point where

08:57.667 --> 08:59.125
Tessa felt like
she had no choice

08:59.208 --> 09:01.417
but to end her
chemotherapy entirely.

09:01.500 --> 09:03.917
Tessa, you chose to
give up the treatment.

09:03.958 --> 09:05.750
